      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEEP THINKER (1) was out of the placings last time when sixth at Geelong (26.48) but scored three back at Bendigo (23.82). Comes through a solid form race last start. Can bounce back. MAGIC BOCCA (5) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including two wins and three placings. Was out of the placings last time (31.36) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing eighth and beaten 12 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. KAELIX STORM (2) finished fourth last time at this track but could not have been more impressive a few runs back in his flying 23.17 win at Horsham over 410m. Should be in this for a long way. ASTON BARRISTER (8) won as expected last time and is a major player again.",
